opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 17th day of August, 2009, the Order of the Commonwealth Court is hereby AFFIRMED. Appellants’ Motion for Oral Argument is DENIED.
Madame Justice TODD did not participate in the consideration or decision of this case.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
